<div class="container">
  <div class="row margin-top-20">
    
    {{!-- expert help from mentors  --}}
    <div class="col s12">
      <h4 class="deep-orange-text">Expert Help From Mentors</h4>
      
      {{#md-card-panel bodyClass="black-text" class="z-depth-2 margin-top-20"}}
      <p>
        Our mentors are Ember.js experts passionate about helping you improve your code and are all active contributors in the Ember.js ecosystem.
      </p>
      <p>
        <ol>
          <li>Get help with an ember problem now.</li>
          <li>Refactor your code.</li>
          <li>Get advice on app architecture.</li>
        </ol>
      </p>
      {{/md-card-panel}}
    </div>
  </div>
  {{!-- end expert help from mentors --}}
  
  {{!-- invest in your team --}}
  <div class="row margin-top-20">
    <div class="col s12">
      <h4 class="deep-orange-text">Invest in Your Team Today.</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="col s12 m6 l6">
      {{#md-card class="z-depth-2" title="Pairing Sessions"}}
      {{#md-card-content}}
      Get an expert to look at your code, suggest improvements, and help you refactor your code making it simpler, more flexible and more efficient.
      <div class="button-container">
        <a href="https://squareup.com/appointments/book/0badee89-09fd-43d2-b7eb-d9b2939e3a49/start?service_id=366dbf19-20c1-4e8a-bff0-9fb8ef67039b" class="btn btn-large orange">Book a Free Pairing</a>
      </div>
      {{/md-card-content}}
      {{/md-card}}
    </div>
    <div class="col s12 m6 l6">
      {{#md-card class="z-depth-2" title="Office Hours"}}
      {{#md-card-content}}
      Starting a new project or need advice on how to move forward with your existing code base? Talking to a mentor and working through the problem can give you confidence to move forward.
      <div class="button-container">
        <a href="https://squareup.com/appointments/book/0badee89-09fd-43d2-b7eb-d9b2939e3a49/start?service_id=4c50e848-71d3-44ba-9182-42fc2e224ad8" class="btn btn-large orange">Book Free Advice</a>
      </div>
      {{/md-card-content}}
      {{/md-card}}
    </div>
  </div>
  {{!-- end invest in your team --}}
  {{!-- mentors --}}
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col s12">
      <h4 class="deep-orange-text">Mentors</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      {{#each model as |mentor|}}
      {{mentor-card mentor=mentor}}
      {{/each}}
    </div>
  </div>
